title: Deal or No Deal: Celebrity Jackpot
overview: Deal or No Deal is set to return to Australian screens with a celebrity twist. Starting Monday, 22 July 2024, at 7.30 pm on 10 and 10 Play, six celebrity jackpot specials will see well-known names take on the Banker.Host Grant Denyer will be joined by Gold Logie-winning comedian Tom Gleeson, MasterChef Australia judges Andy Allen and Sofia Levin, the stars of Gogglebox Australia, Collingwood Premiership captain Darcy Moore, Matildas champion Kyah Simon, and I'm A Celebrityâ€¦ Get Me Out Of Here! winner Skye Wheatley.The celebrities will be aiming to win $250,000 for their chosen charities, adding a feel-good twist to the high-stakes, high-tension format.
